title: The Libs Are Dangerous
description: Fellas discuss the attempted murder of Justice Kavanaugh before breaking down the media's gameplan to amplify Dem Jan 6 messaging. The progrum welcomes Chad Wolf for a conversation about his work as the former Secretary of Homeland Security. And Breitbart writer Allum Bokhari joins for an interview.
